---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Team | AI‑Native.es"
  description="An international team led by Eric Martinez Solis and Victor, bringing a decade of European product and growth experience back to Spain."
>
  <section class="px-6 pb-20 pt-16 md:pt-24">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl text-center" data-animation="fade-up">
      <p class="mb-3 text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.28em] text-cyan-300">
        The team
      </p>
      <h1 class="mb-4 text-3xl font-bold md:text-5xl">People behind AI‑Native.es</h1>
      <p class="mx-auto max-w-3xl text-zinc-400">
        We started AI‑Native.es after a decade of working inside large European organisations. Now we’re using that
        experience to help Spanish companies move faster, with senior hands actually on the work.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mx-auto mt-16 grid max-w-6xl gap-8 md:grid-cols-2" data-animation="fade-up">
      <article class="space-y-3 rounded-2xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900/60 p-6">
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-cyan-300">Co‑founder · Product & Design</p>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">Eric Martinez Solis</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
          Design Director specialising in product design, research, and experimentation. Eric has led design and
          research for €100M+ platforms across Europe, including Flaconi, KFZteile24, Vodafone, eBay, and Dunnhumby.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
          He’s at his best in complex environments – aligning leadership, product, and engineering, and turning UX into
          a measurable growth lever rather than a “nice to have”.
        </p>
        <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500">
          Based in Berlin, originally from Spain, Eric splits his time between European product teams and Spanish
          clients who want that same level of rigour.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="space-y-3 rounded-2xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900/60 p-6">
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-cyan-300">Co‑founder · AI‑native CTO</p>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">Victor</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
          Victor is the technical backbone of AI‑Native.es – an entrepreneurial CTO comfortable bridging modern
          front‑end, cloud, and AI‑driven workflows. He ensures that every idea we design can be implemented cleanly and
          performantly.
        </p>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
          His focus: pragmatic architectures, solid data foundations, and using AI where it genuinely reduces friction
          instead of adding noise.
        </p>
        <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500">
          Originally from Spain and based in Europe, Victor has spent the last decade building and scaling digital
          products internationally.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="space-y-3 rounded-2xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900/60 p-6">
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-cyan-300">SEO & Organic Growth</p>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">Belinda</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
          Belinda focuses on organic visibility, technical SEO, and content strategy. She connects what people actually
          search for with how your product is presented – both to users and to search engines.
        </p>
        <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500">
          Working closely with Eric and Victor, she makes sure technical decisions, IA, and content all pull in the same
          direction.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="space-y-3 rounded-2xl border border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-900/60 p-6">
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-cyan-300">SEA, Brand & Performance</p>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold">Katja</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-zinc-400">
          Katja leads paid search and performance marketing, with a strong brand and creative sensibility. She treats
          SEA as part of a broader system – aligned with UX, content, and analytics – rather than an isolated channel.
        </p>
        <p class="text-xs text-zinc-500">
          Her work is about clarity and control: knowing where budget goes, why it performs, and how to scale
          sustainably.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>

    <div class="mx-auto mt-16 max-w-4xl text-center" data-animation="fade-up">
      <h2 class="mb-3 text-2xl font-semibold">International mindset, Spanish focus</h2>
      <p class="mb-6 text-sm text-zinc-400">
        We’ve all spent years working abroad, inside teams that operate at scale. AI‑Native.es is our way of bringing
        that standard back home – to Spanish companies who want serious, senior partners rather than generic “AI”
        agencies.
      </p>
      <a
        href="/contact"
        class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg bg-cyan-400 px-8 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-950 transition-colors hover:bg-cyan-300"
      >
        Meet the team on a call
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

